texts.content: {"text":"8. Va ammo, kimki baxillik va istig`no qilsa...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"13. Albatta, ham oxirat va ham bu dunyo Biznikidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"17. Va albatta, undan taqvodor banda chetda qoladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,52]}]}

{"text":"19. Biror kishining unda qaytarilishi lozim yaxshiligi yo`q edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"20. Faqat, o`zining oliy maqom Robbining roziligini so`rab qiladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,67]}]}
